{"turn_id":4,"timestamp":"2026-04-29T02:35:32.262955+00:00","speaker":"bob","content":"好了，准备工作都做完了。现在咖啡馆已经收拾得整整齐齐，咖啡的香气也在空气中飘散开来。我就先坐在柜台后面，一边擦拭着咖啡杯，一边等着看看今天会有哪些老顾客来光顾。这个小镇的早晨总是很安静，但过不了多久，熟客们就会陆续推门进来了。","is_folded":false,"folded_from":null,"metadata":{"source":"town_dialogue","location_id":"cafe","clock_minute":510}}
{"turn_id":5,"timestamp":"2026-04-29T02:36:04.548391+00:00","speaker":"bob","content":"已提交动作：wait","is_folded":false,"folded_from":null,"metadata":{"source":"town_dialogue","location_id":"cafe","clock_minute":520}}
{"turn_id":6,"timestamp":"2026-04-29T02:36:52.204012+00:00","speaker":"bob","content":"早上好，Alice！今天来得真早啊。我刚把咖啡馆收拾好，咖啡也试过了，味道还不错。要不要来一杯？","is_folded":false,"folded_from":null,"metadata":{"source":"town_speech","location_id":"cafe","clock_minute":540,"target_npc_id":"alice"}}
