{"turn_id":8,"timestamp":"2026-04-29T02:37:18.402303+00:00","speaker":"bob","content":"早上好，Alice！今天来得真早啊。我刚把咖啡馆收拾好，咖啡也试过了，味道还不错。要不要来一杯？","is_folded":false,"folded_from":null,"metadata":{"source":"town_speech","location_id":"cafe","clock_minute":550,"target_npc_id":"alice"}}
